-Purpose Autonomy":[51,52],"#Autonomous Agents#⚠️ Sharp Edges":[53,65],"#Autonomous Agents#⚠️ Sharp Edges#{1}":[55,65],"#Autonomous Agents#Related Skills":[66,69],"#Autonomous Agents#Related Skills#{1}":[68,69]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"name":"autonomous-agents","description":"Autonomous agents are AI systems that can independently decompose goals, plan actions, execute tools, and self-correct without constant human guidance. The challenge isn't making them capable - it's making them reliable. Every extra decision multiplies failure probability.  This skill covers agent loops (ReAct, Plan-Execute), goal decomposition, reflection patterns, and production reliability. Key insight: compounding error rates kill autonomous agents. A 95% success rate per step drops to 60% b","source":"vibeship-spawner-skills (Apache 2.0)"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"00_System/Links/App_agent_skills_repo/autonomous-agents/SKILL.md"},
